reviewText: If you're into sci-fi for the writing and the acting. A true sci-fi fan. Intellectually then you will understand & appreciate the gem this movie is.

A very well thought out movie and worthy of watching.  I'd suggest the movie be released online thru amazon.com for streaming immediately.  There is rare talent in this movie. I'd recommend watching this movie on a cold wet damp night.  Something to get you into the thriller and excitement mood.  Great Story Line, I plan on watching this movie when I have time.
